| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7418 — Mass File Rename (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 23d386a3-c975-5a55-8ed9-1482e66ed278"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
